| TSPWrapper                | "[points] output [sol]" | ``tsplib`` |
| **Graph Tasks** |
| (Graph)Wrapper            | "[edge_index] label [sol]" | ``gpickle`` |
| (Graph)Wrapper [weighted] | "[edge_index] weights [weights] label [sol]" | ``gpickle`` |
